node.text: When you harbor negative emotions internally they’ll project themselves into the physical. When you internalize love, peace, harmony, & gratitude inside your external world will be filled with reasons to be happy and fulfilled. Be careful what you think about and the emotions you FEEL inside. Our internal world is merely a mirror of our physical world. Choose positive emotions and vibrations and you’ll attract the life you desire. #AM

node.title: Your outside world is a reflection of your inside world.

node.text: You’ve got to be biggest supporter and #1 fan. Before the marketplace, your friends and family, or respected individuals in business believe in you, you must believe in you. When I was 21 I began telling myself over and over and over and over and over that “I AM A MILLIONAIRE BY 25”. I said everyday, all day long, in my head, out loud, I wrote it down, I saw it, felt it, and embodied it. Every “rank” I’ve ever achieved I did the same thing.. I professed it over and over and over again. I have used affirmations for over a decade to get what I want. What you want also wants you but you must call it’s name through repetition and energy!! Now I profess I AM SO HAPPY AND GRATEFUL TO HAVE AN AMAZING, LOVING, LOYAL FAMILY AND SO GRATEFUL TO BE HAPPILY MARRIED 99 YEARS WITH 2-4 FOUR AMAZING KIDS!! I AM SO GRATEFUL TO BE CHANGING THE LIVES OF MILLIONS OF PEOPLE THROUGH MY WORDS, ACTIONS, & PERSON. I am grateful to have helped create 1000 millionaires!! WHY NOT???? I see it, taste it, feel it, become it!! The future is always RIGHT HERE. We create the next scene of our lives by our words, images, and emotions!! Use this affirmation to get yourself into the right frequency, energy, & vibration!! #AM #Success

node.text: I was once that young kid with a few dollars and a dream.. sitting in the front row of the events taking notes until my hands were callused all over, not taking bathroom breaks between speakers, & bringing my own lunch into the venue so I never had to leave. I was once that young kid walking up to every 6/7 figure earner asking for “one piece of advice”… at this point in my career I do it for that young kid with a dream!! The dream is alive for anyone willing to work hard, I believe that! You can come from any background and you can be any skin color and the dream is alive for you! Never stop dreaming! I’m still that young kid dreaming big but now instead of 6/8 figure earners I’m looking up to people like Bob Proctor, Tony Robbins, & Grant Cardone.. because that’s the next floor on the hotel!! It’s already done & I want all the young kids to know that the dream is alive and better than ever!! Work hard and believe!!!! #AM

node.text: If you want FREEDOM go and get your freedom. Stop waiting for permission or waiting for someone to “bail” you out financially. Only YOU control your destiny. Make the decision today to stop playing small and start to THINK BIG & work hard consistently!! #AM

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Alex Morton in 𝓊𝓃𝓀𝓃𝑜𝓌𝓃 with @lunaaileh. May be a black-and-white image of 1 person and standing.

node.text: The years and years of sacrifice and hard work will be worth it when you can do as you please with the people you love. When I was 21 someone told me, “Alex, wealthy people don’t take vacations, they simply live their lives in different parts of the world.” Keep dreaming, believing, working, & never give up. Your time is close!! #AM

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Alex Morton on August 16, 2021 tagging @casejkeppin_______, @mateogribbly, @disframe, and @loganholle. May be an image of 1 person and text that says '"You can't control how tall you are or what you look like, but you can control your degree of obsession and Nortin level of work ethic. am here today because changed my paradigm, and I've been obsessed with the work, the process, the journey, and the game of success for over a decade now."'.

node.text: Only focus on things that you can directly influence and control. The world is a noisy place and it’s easy to get distracted.. put your energy towards becoming the best version of yourself. Work on your inner game as well as your outside game. Success is predictable and can be yours when you play the game in adherence to the laws of the universe. Stay Blessed. #AM

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Alex Morton on August 14, 2021 tagging @mateogribbly, @disframe, and @pantheonlimited. May be an image of 3 people and people standing.

node.text: We frequently don’t do what we already know how to do. That’s the problem when it comes to people reaching success. You don’t need to learn new information right away, you need to delete certain files in your mind and then replace them with new ideas, habits, belief systems, thought patterns, self image, self confidence, & visualizations. When your mind is finally programmed right it will automatically tell your body what actions to take, and your results will change like night and day. I went from $0 to over $1M in under 2 years back in 2011-2013. HOW? I de programmed my mind and then reprogrammed it for success. YOU CAN AS WELL. #AM
